        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><p>title: Hexo简易博客搭建教程<br>tag: 学习<br>category:   </p><ul><li>环境搭建  </li><li>博客搭建<br>cover:  <a href="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87/Hexo%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2.jpg">https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/图片/Hexo封面.jpg</a><br>date: 2023-09-10 00:00:00</li></ul><hr><h1 id="相关地址"><a href="#相关地址" class="headerlink" title="相关地址"></a>相关地址</h1><ul><li>Node下载地址:<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download">https://nodejs.org/en/download</a></li><li>Git下载路径:<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></li><li>butterfly官方地址:<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">https://butterfly.js.org</a></li><li>参考图标网站:<a href="https://fontawesome.com/v4/icons">https://fontawesome.com/v4/icons</a></li></ul><h1 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h1><h2 id="安装必要工具"><a href="#安装必要工具" class="headerlink" title="安装必要工具"></a>安装必要工具</h2><h3 id="Node-js安装"><a href="#Node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="Node.js安装"></a>Node.js安装</h3><ul><li>进入Node官网下载最新版本的Node，具体查看相关[[#相关地址|地址]]<br>   <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/Node%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85.png"></li><li>按照以下步骤安装Node<br>   一路点击next即可，可以自己选择安装路径</li><li>检查是否安装成功node<br>✨进入CMD窗口，敲击&#x3D;&#x3D;node -v&#x3D;&#x3D;,如果出现以下版本信息，表示node安装成功了<br>  <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/Node%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF.png"></li><li>检查是否安装成功npm<br>✨同样，进入CMD窗口，敲击&#x3D;&#x3D;npm -v&#x3D;&#x3D;<br>   <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/npm%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png"></li><li>修改npm的镜像源<br>   <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2npm%E7%9A%84%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E6%BA%90.png"><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Git安装"><a href="#Git安装" class="headerlink" title="Git安装"></a>Git安装</h3><ul><li>从[[#相关地址|地址]]中找到Git的下载地址，下载Git<br>  <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDGit.png"><br>  <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDGit2.png"></li><li>安装git<br>   一路点击next即可，可以自己选择安装路径</li><li>检查自己的git是否正常安装<br>  <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5git%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85.png"><br>  <img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/Gitbash.png"></li></ul><h3 id="Hexo安装"><a href="#Hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装"></a>Hexo安装</h3><ul><li><p>安装Hexo<br>  ✨注意这里要选定一个你自己的blog目录，否则后续操作会因为没有target而报错</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85hexo.png"></p></li><li><p>hexo初始化配置<br>  ✨不知道为什么下面的初始化会很卡，关键我上了梯子还是很卡</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init </span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/init%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png"></p></li><li><p>检查本地博客是否搭建完成</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate(hexo g)</span><br><span class="line">hexo server(hexo s)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png"><br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/hexo%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2.png"></p></li></ul><h2 id="本地博客的部署"><a href="#本地博客的部署" class="headerlink" title="本地博客的部署"></a>本地博客的部署</h2><p>我们用github来存储管理我们的博客</p><h3 id="新建博客"><a href="#新建博客" class="headerlink" title="新建博客"></a>新建博客</h3><ul><li>打开github，点击New，创建一个仓库<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93.png"></li><li>更改仓库名称<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93.png" alt="创建仓库"></li></ul><h3 id="配置SSH密钥"><a href="#配置SSH密钥" class="headerlink" title="配置SSH密钥"></a>配置SSH密钥</h3><p>用于远程登陆自己的仓库</p><ul><li>点击设置<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BBsetting.png"></li><li>创建SSH密钥<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BASSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5.png"></li><li>配置SSH密钥<br>  需要在你的博客终端配置ssh密钥<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5.png"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A52.png"></p><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A53.png"></p><ul><li>复制SSH公钥<br>   在上图配置SSH密钥的时候 ，我们可以找到公钥的存储位置<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clip &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>填写密钥标识，点击创建<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BASSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A53.png"></li><li>检查是否创建成功<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png"></li><li>测试是否配置成功<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.con</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png"></li></ul><h3 id="配置GIt的个人信息"><a href="#配置GIt的个人信息" class="headerlink" title="配置GIt的个人信息"></a>配置GIt的个人信息</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;Baimusheng&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;cfrankm2022@outlook.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署博客"><a href="#部署博客" class="headerlink" title="部署博客"></a>部署博客</h3><ul><li>获取github上面项目代码库的ssh路径<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84SSH%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84.png"></li><li>修改_config.yml的代码<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9config%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.png"></li><li>将代码部署到git上<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -d </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="域名设置"><a href="#域名设置" class="headerlink" title="域名设置"></a>域名设置</h2><h3 id="购买一个域名"><a href="#购买一个域名" class="headerlink" title="购买一个域名"></a>购买一个域名</h3><p>有很多网站上可以购买域名，可以是阿里云，或者腾讯云，也可是其他网站，那些比较便宜，我用的是阿里云的域名<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0.png" alt="域名购买"></p><h3 id="等待注册局审核"><a href="#等待注册局审核" class="headerlink" title="等待注册局审核"></a>等待注册局审核</h3><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%B1%80%E5%AE%A1%E6%A0%B8.png" alt="注册局审核"></p><h3 id="添加网站到Cloudflare"><a href="#添加网站到Cloudflare" class="headerlink" title="添加网站到Cloudflare"></a>添加网站到Cloudflare</h3><p>可以保护你的网站，让别人更fast的加载你的网站~选择免费版，不白嫖是傻子</p><ul><li>注册cloudflare<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8CCloudflare%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7.png" alt="注册Cloudflare账号"></li><li>添加网站<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99.png" alt="添加网站"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%992.png" alt="添加网站2"></p><ul><li>选择免费版<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%89%88.png" alt="选择免费版"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%B7%9F%E6%8D%A2%E7%9A%84DNS%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1.png" alt="记录需要跟换的DNS服务"></p><ul><li>将原来网站的DNS服务替换成CloudFlare的<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D.png" alt="管理域名"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9DNS.png" alt="修改DNS"></p><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9DNS2.png" alt="修改DNS2"></p><ul><li>进Cloudflare中check nameservers<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/checknameservers.png" alt="checknameservers"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/checknameservers2.png" alt="checknameservers2"></p><ul><li>邮件通知设置成功<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5.png" alt="邮件通知"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%92%8CAAAA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95.png" alt="设置A记录和AAAA记录"></p><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%88%B0Cloudflare%E4%B8%8A2.png" alt="添加记录到Cloudflare上2"></p><h3 id="配置好自己域名的DNS解析"><a href="#配置好自己域名的DNS解析" class="headerlink" title="配置好自己域名的DNS解析"></a>配置好自己域名的DNS解析</h3><ul><li>根据GIthub文档设置A记录和AAAA记录<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3.png" alt="设置域名和查看文档"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%92%8CAAAA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95.png" alt="设置A记录和AAAA记录"></p><p>注意，下图的代理是没有打开的<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%88%B0Cloudflare%E4%B8%8A2.png" alt="添加记录到Cloudflare上2"></p><ul><li>在github填写自己的新的域名<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%9C%A8github%E4%B8%8A%E5%A1%AB%E5%86%99%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D.png" alt="在github上填写域名"></li><li>等待DNS check 成功，这个需要一段时间，我等了差不多1个小时<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/dnsCheck.png" alt="dnsCheck"></li><li>修改_config.yml文件中的域名<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%9C%A8blog%E4%B8%8A%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEurl.png" alt="在blog上设置url"></li><li>启动cloudflare中的代理<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86.png" alt="打开代理"></li><li>刷新电脑的DNS缓存<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ipconfig /flushdns</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0DNS%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98.png" alt="刷新DNS缓存"></li></ul><h2 id="主题选择"><a href="#主题选择" class="headerlink" title="主题选择"></a>主题选择</h2><h3 id="安装Butterfly主题"><a href="#安装Butterfly主题" class="headerlink" title="安装Butterfly主题"></a>安装Butterfly主题</h3><ul><li>下载Butterfly主题，在文件的根目录<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDbutterfly%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98.png"></li><li>修改根目录下的.config.yml文件中的 theme<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98.png"></li><li>需要安装pug和stylus的渲染器<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E5%99%A8.png"></li><li>创建_config.butterfly.yml<br>   hexo主题会主动合并_config.yml和_config.butterfly.yml文件里面的配置，&#x3D;&#x3D;注意是主题的_config.yml&#x3D;&#x3D;,并且_config.butterfly.yml的优先级比较高，这个之后butterfly就已经安装完成了~<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA_config_butterfly_yml%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.png"></li><li>测试是否安装完成<ul><li>hexo g -d </li><li>hexo s<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90.png"></li></ul></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/butterfly_hexo.png"></p><h2 id="常见配置"><a href="#常见配置" class="headerlink" title="常见配置"></a>常见配置</h2><h3 id="修改界面语言"><a href="#修改界面语言" class="headerlink" title="修改界面语言"></a>修改界面语言</h3><p>修改文件: config.yml</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">百木生</span>                                     <span class="comment">#文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;追求心流&#x27;</span>                              <span class="comment">#文章副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;愿有春风常盈袖，心中百木向阳生&#x27;</span>       <span class="comment">#网页描述</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">肥宅,技术宅,菜鸟,永恒的梦想者,不断前进</span>    <span class="comment">#关键词</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">chenlihao</span>                                <span class="comment">#作者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span>                                  <span class="comment">#语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>                                     <span class="comment">#时区</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">email:</span> <span class="string">cfrankm2022@outlook.com</span>                   <span class="comment">#邮箱</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码栏显示"><a href="#代码栏显示" class="headerlink" title="代码栏显示"></a>代码栏显示</h3><p>修改文件:_config_butterfly_yml</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_theme:</span> <span class="string">ocean</span>            <span class="comment">#主题推荐 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_copy:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>              <span class="comment">#代码是否可以复制</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_lang:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>              <span class="comment">#代码语言显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_shrink:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>           <span class="comment">#代码是否折叠</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_height_limit:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>     <span class="comment">#代码行高限制</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">code_word_wrap:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>             <span class="comment">#是否可以换行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="导航菜单"><a href="#导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="导航菜单"></a>导航菜单</h3><ul><li>修改_config_butterfly_yml文件</li><li>语法解释: || 的左边是路径，右边是图标</li><li>具体图标地址修改可以参考[[#相关地址|地址]]中的图标地址<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">主页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-folder-open</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">列表||fas</span> <span class="attr">fa-list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">音乐:</span> <span class="string">/music/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-music</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">电影:</span> <span class="string">/movies/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-video</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Archives: /archives/ || fas fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Link: /link/ || fas fa-link</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># About: /about/ || fas fa-heart</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%952.png"></li></ul><h3 id="创建标签页"><a href="#创建标签页" class="headerlink" title="创建标签页"></a>创建标签页</h3><ul><li>创建一个新的标签页<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">new</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">tags</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>之后可以找到source&#x2F;tags&#x2F;index.md这个文件<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E9%A1%B5.png"><br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E9%A1%B5.png"></li></ul><h3 id="创建分类页"><a href="#创建分类页" class="headerlink" title="创建分类页"></a>创建分类页</h3><ul><li>创建一个新的分类页<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">new</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">categories</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>创建完成之后就能找到source&#x2F;categories&#x2F;index.md文件<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E9%A1%B52.png"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E9%A1%B5.png"></p><h3 id="文章上传相关设置"><a href="#文章上传相关设置" class="headerlink" title="文章上传相关设置"></a>文章上传相关设置</h3><p>可以将文章配合标签页和分类页进行上传,将下面的代码放到文章的最上面</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可以将上传的文章进行分类  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Hexo简易博客搭建教程</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tag:</span> <span class="string">学习</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">category:</span>   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">环境搭建</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">博客搭建</span>    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="string">上传时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cover:</span>  <span class="string">图片地址</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置文章链接数字转字母"><a href="#配置文章链接数字转字母" class="headerlink" title="配置文章链接数字转字母"></a>配置文章链接数字转字母</h3><p>可以便于后续搜索文章</p><ul><li>参考安装路径:<a href="https://github.com/rozbo/hexo-abbrlink">https://github.com/rozbo/hexo-abbrlink</a><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>修改_config.yml文件，将后缀改成.html<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%90%8E%E7%BC%80%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png"></li><li>未修改<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%90%8E%E7%BC%801.png"></li><li>修改后<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%90%8E%E7%BC%802.png"></li></ul><h3 id="本地搜索功能"><a href="#本地搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索功能"></a>本地搜索功能</h3><ul><li>安装hexo-generator-search</li><li>参考安装路径:<a href="https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-generator-search">https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-generator-search</a><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo-generator-search</span> <span class="string">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>修改_config.yml文件<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#本地搜索功能</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">all</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>修改_config_butterfly_yml文件<br>   打开本地搜索功能<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%BD%BF%E8%83%BD.png"></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA.png"></p><h3 id="Butterfly侧边栏修改"><a href="#Butterfly侧边栏修改" class="headerlink" title="Butterfly侧边栏修改"></a>Butterfly侧边栏修改</h3><ul><li>修改_config.butterfly.yml文件的aside<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#修改公告内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">card_announcement:</span>  </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>  </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="string">桃花流水窅然去，别有天地非人间</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png" alt="侧边栏修改"></li></ul><h2 id="博客美化"><a href="#博客美化" class="headerlink" title="博客美化"></a>博客美化</h2><h3 id="相关图像修改"><a href="#相关图像修改" class="headerlink" title="相关图像修改"></a>相关图像修改</h3><ul><li>网页背景图片修改<ul><li>修改_config.butterfly.yml中的background字段<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png" alt="背景图片修改"></li></ul></li><li>个人头像修改<ul><li>修改_config.butterfly.yml中的avatar字段<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%A4%B4%E5%83%8F%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png" alt="头像修改"></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="一图流"><a href="#一图流" class="headerlink" title="一图流"></a>一图流</h3><ul><li>在source目录下创建css文件夹，并创建文件custom.css,并添加以下的内容<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">/*top-img黑色透明玻璃效果移除，不建议加，除非你执着于完全一图流或者背景图对比色明显</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#page-header:not(.not-top-img):before &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background-color:</span> <span class="string">transparent</span> <span class="type">!important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">首页文章卡片</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#recent-posts &gt; .recent-post-item &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255,</span> <span class="number">255</span><span class="string">,</span> <span class="number">255</span><span class="string">,</span> <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">首页侧栏卡片</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#aside-content .card-widget &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255,</span> <span class="number">255</span><span class="string">,</span> <span class="number">255</span><span class="string">,</span> <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">文章页面正文背景</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">div#post</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">分页页面</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">div#page</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">归档页面</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">div#archive</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">标签页面</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">div#tag</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">分类页面</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">div#category</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">);</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*夜间模式伪类遮罩层透明*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="comment">#recent-posts &gt; .recent-post-item &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">.card-widget</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#post</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#tag</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#archive</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#page</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#category</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="comment">#121212 !important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">  [<span class="string">data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;</span>] <span class="string">div#category</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">transparent</span> <span class="type">!important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">页脚透明</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#footer &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">transparent</span> <span class="type">!important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">/*</span> <span class="string">头图透明</span> <span class="string">*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#page-header &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">transparent</span> <span class="type">!important;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#rightside &gt; div &gt; button &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">border-radius:</span> <span class="string">5px;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>在_config.butterfly.yml中搜索Inject添加以下的代码,引入自定义的css文件<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84CSS%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.png" alt="引入自定义的CSS文件"></li><li>一图流效果展示</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BE%E6%B5%81%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA.png" alt="一图流效果展示"></p><h1 id="问题记录"><a href="#问题记录" class="headerlink" title="问题记录"></a>问题记录</h1><h2 id="重定向次数过多"><a href="#重定向次数过多" class="headerlink" title="重定向次数过多"></a>重定向次数过多</h2><p>这是在DNS解析成功之后出现的，让后我清楚Cookie也没用，即是把所有的记录全部删除也不行，显然和cookie没有关系<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A.png" alt="重定向次数过多"></p><ul><li>解决方法<ul><li>修改Cloudflare中的SSL&#x2F;TLS模式为strict<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9SSL_TLS%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F.png" alt="修改SSL_TLS模式"></li></ul></li><li>原因解释<ul><li>网站参考:<ul><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_37126941/article/details/122540553">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_37126941/article/details/122540553</a></li><li><a href="https://www.shenghuahuancai.com/">https://www.shenghuahuancai.com/</a> 文章链接后缀太长了，直接放他的博客</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p>我们的网站开启的Cloudflare服务，我们作为用户访问，访问的是Cloudflare的服务器，让cloudflare去访问我们的网站，我们访问慢，但是他访问快啊，达到加速和保护的目的<br>Cloudflare的ssl设置有以下4中<br><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Hexo%E7%AE%80%E6%98%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/SSL%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F.png" alt="SSL模式"></p><ul><li>OFF:不开启</li><li>Flexible:默认选择的，当我们用源网站不支持https访问的的时候，cloudflare会通过http协议访问的我们的网站</li><li>Full:当我们的网站支持https的时候，但是网站https的证书和域名不匹配的时候，cloudflare会通过https来访问，但是不会验证证书，即使我们的网站证书验证通过不了，Cloudflare也会通过https来访问我们的网站</li><li>Full(strict)当我们的网站支持http，并且证书有效的时候，Cloudflare会通过Https协议访问，并在过程中验证证书</li></ul><p>默认是Flexible，我们用https协议访问cloudflare，cloudflare用http来访问网站，然后浏览器又将http跳转成https，https又访问cloudflare，形成了一个死循环。就发生了重定向次数过多的现象</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
    
    
